Title: Barefoot at Capefest
Plot: Dawson experiences an identity crisis when Principal Green's daughter Nikki emerges as another aspiring young director, and Joey experiences her own crisis when Dawson won't open up to her about the pain of his parents' divorce. Meanwhile, Jack's first efforts to hit on another guy are rebuffed, Pacey and Andie uncomfortably find themselves sharing the same after school activity, and Jen realizes that she may have passed up the chance at something special with Henry.
GuestStars: Bianca Lawson, Stephen Michael Ayers, Caleb Burress, Tyrone Hicks, William Turell Hodges III, Maribeth Ayers, Lee Norris, Mohamed El Eman, Thad Mace
